 ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler, Arthur</persName><placeName ref="#pmb50">Wien</placeName><date when="1905-05-23" n="01">23. 5. 1905</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><persName ref="#pmb10863">Beer-Hofmann, Richard</persName><placeName ref="#pmb173">Rodaun</placeName><date when="1905-05-23">23. 5. 1905</date></correspAction><correspContext><tei:ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb10863">Beer-Hofmann, Richard</tei:ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1905-05-11_01">Schnitzler an Beer-Hofmann, 11. 5. 1905</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1905-05-25_01">Beer-Hofmann an Schnitzler, 25. 5. 1905</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
